high_descs: Turn and go to the center counter.
Pick up a butter knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Cut the lettuce on the counter.
Put the butter knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the trash can in the corner.
Put the slice of lettuce in the trash can in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right walk forward then turn right facing the side of island
Pick up the bread knife on the island
Turn right walk straight head to the sink counter
Slice the cabbage on the counter
Put the knife on the left side of the counter
Pick up a sliced cabbage
Turn right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the sliced cabbage
Turn left then head to the trash bin on your right
Put the sliced cabbage in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled sliced cabbage in the trash bin

high_descs: Face the door and turn right.  Walk to the other side of the room where the lettuce is sitting on the counter.  Turn right at the lettuce.  Walk to the edge of the counter on the right.  Turn and face the counter on the right.
Grab the knife directly in front.
Turn right and then turn left.  Walk to the other side of the room where the lettuce is sitting.
Slice the head of lettuce.
Put the knife down on the counter next to the sink.
Pick up a slice of the lettuce.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and put the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator next to the egg.  Open the refrigerator door and grab the slice of lettuce.  Close the refrigerator door.
Turn left and walk toward the sink, turn left at the counter and walk to the corner where the recycling bin is sitting.
Put the slice of lettuce in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Cut a slide of lettuce, chill it, and place in recycling bin.
